---
description: Standards for writing react code
globs: *.tsx
---
- avoid using `any`
- avoid type casting - always map
- unknown/any is allowed at the application API boundary
- dont use React.FC
- dont destructure props, prefer `props.property`
- always use functional components
- prefer boostrap/coreui css classnames
- dont use inline styles
- sensible type definition locations - domain goes in `src/types` folder, encapsulated template types can be in file, such as props
- dont use barrel exports (index.ts) - import directly from component files